    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This demo is designed to let you experience selected content from the full version. It offers a few upgrades to help you explore the mechanics, but it does not include all features, such as home deliveries. However, you can still test the core gameplay and get a preview of the full experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/1b69398b34eba8d1b6712a2046895c93.poster.avif?t=1749489068\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/1b69398b34eba8d1b6712a2046895c93.webm?t=1749489068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/1b69398b34eba8d1b6712a2046895c93.mp4?t=1749489068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/0f7e941f53b4e5847981401dd8798080.webp?t=1749489068\" width=498 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start as an ordinary cargo worker and grow your delivery business step by step.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/39572a9c62f5c92dbd69a8d119c0b592.poster.avif?t=1749489068\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/39572a9c62f5c92dbd69a8d119c0b592.webm?t=1749489068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/39572a9c62f5c92dbd69a8d119c0b592.mp4?t=1749489068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/3de49aadf9e81a924a37f8cfc22091ff.webp?t=1749489068\" width=498 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your office for both efficiency and aesthetics. Manage your cargo shelves and ensure a smooth experience for your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/01aa80b85a4730e4fd0fc7c47a96885c.poster.avif?t=1749489068\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/01aa80b85a4730e4fd0fc7c47a96885c.webm?t=1749489068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/01aa80b85a4730e4fd0fc7c47a96885c.mp4?t=1749489068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173330/extras/bc12fc05b850e1078d987e27ebb85ed8.webp?t=1749489068\" width=498 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invest as you earn. Upgrade your store’s physical space, unlock new cargo types, and maximize your profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akama